1
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:29,740
[Episode 24]

2
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:34,180
I just came to ask you something.

3
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:38,880
On Bo's wedding day,
you wanted to stand with Miao Jing, right?

4
00:01:47,621 --> 00:01:51,780
Yi, I know what's going on
between you and Miao Jing.

5
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:54,800
I didn't come here to ask you for anything.

6
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:58,006
I think I've fallen for you.

7
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,241
There's nothing wrong with that.

8
00:02:03,241 --> 00:02:06,780
I can't tell if this feeling is
admiration or dependence.

9
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:08,640
But to me, liking someone means liking someone.

10
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:12,960
Even if Miao Jing were here today,
I'd still say this.

11
00:02:16,154 --> 00:02:17,794
I'm sorry.

12
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:21,880
I don't feel that way about you.

13
00:02:25,380 --> 00:02:28,320
I knew the answer before I came.

14
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,880
But I felt like I had to say it.

15
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:33,700
Once I said it, I felt better.

16
00:02:39,730 --> 00:02:42,200
I put this in the fridge.

17
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:47,120
It's in the fridge. Remember to eat it.
Otherwise, it will just go bad again.

18
00:02:58,020 --> 00:03:02,080
Miao Jing is pretty thoughtful.
Yi, I should get going.

19
00:03:04,113 --> 00:03:05,572
Tu Li.

20
00:03:08,854 --> 00:03:13,254
If you ever need help,
you can still come to me.

21
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,200
Xiao Yu and Ma Yang didn't come out with you?

22
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:15,521
They are still packing up and will be out soon.

23
00:04:15,521 --> 00:04:19,821
Hongshen sent over a file today.
They want the drafts.

24
00:04:19,821 --> 00:04:21,801
It is that urgent?

25
00:04:23,380 --> 00:04:25,640
Foreign trade has shifted a lot lately.

26
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,500
They probably want to catch the boom
over in Lingang

27
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,960
and lock things down as soon as possible.

28
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:34,320
Once the draft is done,
we need to issue the official report.

29
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:37,920
But we still haven't traced the source
of the empty-container data from last time.

30
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,300
We can't rush the schedule like this.

31
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:42,280
Besides...

32
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,295
Anyway, let's stall for time for now.

33
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:05,180
Then let's issue a broad assessment first.

34
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:09,059
It is not final until we issue
the official report anyway.

35
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,140
[Chen Yi: Where did you go?
Are you coming home tonight?]

36
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,260
A text from Chen Yi?

37
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:25,300
Did he upset you again?

38
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,714
Cen Ye.

39
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:33,760
If someone gave up their future
and stability for you,

40
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:38,240
and charged ahead no matter what,
could you accept that?

41
00:05:41,115 --> 00:05:46,461
I think a good relationship is when
two people are evenly matched and truly fit.

42
00:05:46,461 --> 00:05:49,880
If you love someone
to the point of losing your self-respect,

43
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:52,400
then they probably aren't right for each other.

44
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,531
You're so slow.

45
00:06:03,531 --> 00:06:05,412
- We're ready. Let's go.
- I'm exhausted.

46
00:06:05,412 --> 00:06:08,420
- What did you do? We've been waiting for ages.
- We've saved a lot of money.

47
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:12,781
- We redeemed lots of vouchers. It took time.
- I said there was no need. We were in a hurry.

48
00:06:12,781 --> 00:06:13,981
That would be a waste.

49
00:06:13,981 --> 00:06:15,120
Let's go.

50
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,063
- Buckle up.
- Okay.

51
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:31,520
[Diagonal Billiards Club]
You gave me this license plate number.

52
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:34,580
I've got my colleagues following up on it.

53
00:06:34,580 --> 00:06:38,460
As for that boat,
it was likely a seasoned runner from Lingang.

54
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:40,200
They've already mapped out the route.

55
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,300
But these people are too cautious.

56
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:46,026
As soon as we move in,
they stop doing anything concrete.

57
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:51,480
I'm already applying
for inter-departmental cooperation.

58
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:55,500
All you need to do now
is keep a tight watch on him.

59
00:06:59,481 --> 00:07:04,240
If he's hiding something,
he'll slip up sooner or later.

60
00:07:08,556 --> 00:07:09,860
Uncle Zhou.

61
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:12,840
Things aren't like they were six years ago.

62
00:07:16,873 --> 00:07:18,378
I know.

63
00:07:20,308 --> 00:07:21,723
Yi.

64
00:07:21,723 --> 00:07:25,080
You couldn't get it done for him this time.

65
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:27,760
Do you think he'll start suspecting you?

66
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,880
He never trusted me.

67
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,980
So what is there to suspect?

68
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,000
What about Kao?

69
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,160
He's handling all the contacts himself now?

70
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,680
Yeah.

71
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:43,980
Kao helped me when I was at my lowest.

72
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:47,518
They knew that,
so that's why they came after me.

73
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:52,060
They need Kao's power for their overseas route.

74
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:55,540
That's also why I've been able
to stay at Haoyun.

75
00:07:57,260 --> 00:08:00,340
But when they were testing the waters,
you showed up out of nowhere.

76
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:05,800
Knowing how his mind works,
he won't let me stay on it for a while.

77
00:08:11,477 --> 00:08:13,400
That's enough.

78
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:18,400
Don't dig any deeper,
or you might get pulled into our next move.

79
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,995
I understand.

80
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,885
Yi.

81
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:31,480
I know you know what you're doing.

82
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:36,060
Personally, I want you to walk away right now.

83
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:38,900
But as Wen's husband,

84
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:41,909
I also want to say one thing.

85
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,854
Thank you.

86
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,992
Cut the mushy stuff.

87
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:53,111
Don't joke around with me. I'm serious.

88
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,985
Tell me about yourself.

89
00:08:57,740 --> 00:09:00,559
What did you tell Miao Jing?

90
00:09:05,836 --> 00:09:07,026
What?

91
00:09:07,026 --> 00:09:08,715
Did you two fight?

92
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:12,561
She moved out.

93
00:09:13,532 --> 00:09:15,866
She moved out?

94
00:09:15,866 --> 00:09:18,500
She moved out? It's that bad?

95
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:21,780
Then it must be a big deal.
Did you try to make it up to her?

96
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:25,200
If that would fix it,
she wouldn't have moved out.

97
00:09:29,203 --> 00:09:31,342
Wen was the same.

98
00:09:31,342 --> 00:09:34,520
Back then, when I made her mad,

99
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:40,275
if it was something small,
she'd pout and make a fuss.

100
00:09:40,275 --> 00:09:41,920
She would give me a chance to apologize.

101
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:46,460
But when I crossed her line,
she was calmer than anyone.

102
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:50,000
No sweet talk would work.
No apology would work.

103
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,922
Then what do I do?

104
00:09:57,659 --> 00:09:59,086
What do you do?

105
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,547
Wear her down.

106
00:10:01,547 --> 00:10:05,607
Keep apologizing
and find the right moment to do it sincerely.

107
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,580
You little punk.

108
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:11,560
Stop making Miao Jing worry about you.

109
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:14,461
If you always make girls make the first move,
how will you ever find a wife?

110
00:10:14,461 --> 00:10:16,340
Honestly.

111
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:20,421
What are you standing there for? Keep playing.

112
00:10:20,421 --> 00:10:23,982
Beat me, and Miao Jing will come back.

113
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:29,739
I'll go for a long one.

114
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:46,220
Vehicle and vessel tax, property tax,
and land value-added tax are expenses.

115
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:47,840
And they're carried over directly.

116
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:51,721
Resource tax
and consumption tax involve no loss.

117
00:10:51,721 --> 00:10:54,721
- Gosh, I think that's all of them.
- Good heavens.

118
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:59,460
These past two or three months felt like years.

119
00:10:59,460 --> 00:11:00,900
How are things on your end?

120
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:03,721
Finally, there's something to look forward to.

121
00:11:03,721 --> 00:11:08,760
I miss my fresh pork mooncakes,
butterfly pastries, and scallion oil noodles.

122
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:11,255
Hard to tell if you miss people or food.

123
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,920
What did you say?

124
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:18,080
I said once you're back in Hai City,
you'll miss the food here so much.

125
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,540
Rice noodle rolls, wontons, and beef balls.

126
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:25,480
Ma Yang.

127
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:28,201
What? Don't look at me like that. I'm scared.

128
00:11:28,201 --> 00:11:29,981
I think you've got real potential.

129
00:11:29,981 --> 00:11:31,260
What kind of potential?

130
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:33,780
The potential to hang out with Ding Lei.

131
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:37,660
Being annoying is also a talent.

132
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:39,224
Boss.

133
00:11:39,224 --> 00:11:40,960
She's picking on me.

134
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,301
I won't eat with her tonight.
I'll eat with you instead.

135
00:11:43,301 --> 00:11:46,300
Don't push your luck. I have plans tonight.

136
00:11:48,441 --> 00:11:51,481
You think everyone is like you?

137
00:11:51,481 --> 00:11:56,800
Jing already told me.
She's meeting someone tonight.

138
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:59,220
Well, who do you think the guy is?

139
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:04,000
Boss, you get to be happy again.

140
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:07,820
Everyone, go grab dinner.
After dinner, we need to finish this batch.

141
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:09,740
- Overtime!
- No.

142
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,780
You did threaten someone else's interests.

143
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,961
Been busy lately?

144
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:35,580
You haven't had time to come by
and fish or play pool with me.

145
00:12:37,308 --> 00:12:39,300
Just regular work.

146
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:42,420
My workload is up to you, isn't it?

147
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:45,500
Mr. Liu called to thank you.

148
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:48,841
The shipment almost drew police attention.

149
00:12:48,841 --> 00:12:53,260
Thanks to you working both ends,
we dodged a bullet.

150
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:54,680
Chen Yi.

151
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:58,081
Are you really on my side?

152
00:12:58,081 --> 00:12:59,620
What do you think, Mr. Zhang?

153
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:01,500
Of course, I trust you.

154
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:06,840
After all these years,
the two of us have been through a lot together.

155
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:11,680
For the company to get this far,
you deserve a lot of the credit.

156
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:15,040
Take a look at this.

157
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:24,620
These audit risk alerts keep getting worse.

158
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:30,920
I was worried something might go wrong
and affect the plan with Hongshen.

159
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,080
But I spoke with Miao Jing.

160
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:38,582
She said she can take full responsibility
for the results of this audit.

161
00:13:40,060 --> 00:13:42,460
[Auditor: Miao Jing]

162
00:13:48,293 --> 00:13:51,581
I'm glad I have you both helping me.

163
00:13:51,581 --> 00:13:53,060
Chen Yi.

164
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:56,760
Remember. We're family.

165
00:13:58,260 --> 00:14:00,600
We're in this together, for life.

166
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:12,340
[Haoyun Logistics]

167
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:24,080
Any other questions, Mr. Chen?

168
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:28,240
I've reviewed all these reports.
They're very clear.

169
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:30,913
There are just a few points I don't get.

170
00:14:30,913 --> 00:14:32,600
Go ahead.

171
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:36,260
Aren't these risk ratings too severe?

172
00:14:36,260 --> 00:14:40,680
As the auditor, I have to ensure
the audit results are fair and accurate.

173
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:45,820
We're simply giving an objective warning
about possible risks and loopholes.

174
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:49,640
Of course, this assessment is only
for Hongshen Group.

175
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:55,000
So they can assess if Haoyun can operate well
during the investment period.

176
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:59,080
Looks like
auditing really does take skill and guts.

177
00:15:06,221 --> 00:15:07,961
<i>The tension in here is intense.</i>

178
00:15:07,961 --> 00:15:11,153
<i>What is going on?
Isn't the project almost over?</i>

179
00:15:12,181 --> 00:15:13,481
<i>I get it.</i>

180
00:15:13,481 --> 00:15:17,360
<i>This is the final showdown
before the competency project audit wraps up.</i>

181
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:20,701
<i>The whole point is to own the room.</i>

182
00:15:20,701 --> 00:15:23,760
<i>Jing is choosing duty over family.</i>

183
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,720
<i>Respect.</i>

184
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:36,339
Will Mr. Cen follow up on this project?

185
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:42,217
Since you think the reports are fine,
then you simply don't trust me.

186
00:15:42,217 --> 00:15:45,960
You don't trust me to handle this project.

187
00:15:48,332 --> 00:15:49,853
Of course, I trust you.

188
00:15:49,853 --> 00:15:52,020
I trust you, too.

189
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:55,920
Then we share the risk.
The project can wrap up sooner.

190
00:15:58,090 --> 00:16:01,840
If there are no other issues,
today's meeting is adjourned.

191
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:04,320
The audit is actually nearly finished.

192
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:07,087
We also hope to wrap this project up soon.

193
00:16:07,087 --> 00:16:11,789
That way, Mr. Chen won't have to
work so hard at Haoyun.

194
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:23,800
Why sign the audit form?

195
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,441
Once you sign,
you're taking full responsibility.

196
00:16:26,441 --> 00:16:29,000
- Do you know what that means?
- I do.

197
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,400
That's why I have to sign.

198
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:37,201
I was wrong before.

199
00:16:37,201 --> 00:16:40,140
If you move out or choose to go back
to Hai City, I won't stop you.

200
00:16:40,140 --> 00:16:43,120
But don't take this risk.
I'm afraid I can't protect you.

201
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:46,480
- Isn't this trip a risk for you, too?
- That's different.

202
00:16:50,573 --> 00:16:51,839
Miao Jing.

203
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:54,380
I thought there were many things
I shouldn't tell you.

204
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:56,640
So I kept them from you. I'm sorry.

205
00:16:58,160 --> 00:17:00,420
But Zhang Bin is far more dangerous
than you realize.

206
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:02,740
Far more dangerous
than anything you've faced in an audit.

207
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:05,020
I know exactly what I'm doing.

208
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:08,394
Chen Yi.

209
00:17:09,024 --> 00:17:12,940
I'm not who I used to be.
But you're still stuck in the past.

210
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,620
You always think you have to protect me.

211
00:17:14,620 --> 00:17:18,790
But have you ever thought
that I don't need your protection anymore?

212
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:33,700
Come with me to check the files.

213
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:51,540
<i>You always think you have to protect me.</i>

214
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:55,820
<i>But have you ever thought
that I don't need your protection anymore?</i>

215
00:17:58,126 --> 00:18:01,020
[Haoyun Logistics]
I told you last night. Do handle it for me.

216
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:03,495
Mr. Cen, we're heading out.

217
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:06,040
Let's go eat.

218
00:18:18,238 --> 00:18:19,727
Cen Ye.

219
00:18:29,461 --> 00:18:30,560
Uncle Zhou.

220
00:18:30,560 --> 00:18:32,531
No need to be so formal with me.

221
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:40,340
You've been back for a while,
but I haven't even taken you out for a bite.

222
00:18:40,340 --> 00:18:44,080
I happen to have the day off today.
It's not too late to make up for it, is it?

223
00:18:44,080 --> 00:18:47,171
Of course not.
I should be visiting you more often.

224
00:18:48,311 --> 00:18:52,477
I'm not that old.
No need to talk about visits with me.

225
00:18:52,477 --> 00:18:55,660
- Here. Have some porridge.
- Thank you.

226
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:59,460
You didn't invite Chen Yi today?

227
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:03,520
Aren't you two having a fight?

228
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:07,780
If I called him over,
wouldn't that make me the peacemaker?

229
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:10,860
That's an old man's job, not mine.

230
00:19:13,627 --> 00:19:15,000
Jing.

231
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:18,320
How long will you be busy this time?

232
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:23,499
You mean how much longer
my audit at Haoyun will take?

233
00:19:25,120 --> 00:19:29,040
Are you asking, or is Chen Yi?

234
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:32,240
That kid doesn't have the nerve
to send me to pry it out of you.

235
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:34,220
I'm the one asking.

236
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:38,280
That depends on how cooperative Chen Yi is.

237
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:40,201
Actually, I wanted to ask last time.

238
00:19:40,201 --> 00:19:45,060
What exactly are Chen Yi and you
doing now with Haoyun?

239
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,560
Hot.

240
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:51,701
Jing.

241
00:19:52,820 --> 00:19:55,420
What kind of person do you think Chen Yi is?

242
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:57,540
What do you mean?

243
00:19:58,620 --> 00:20:01,020
If he'd gotten into the police academy,

244
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:05,234
and had to carry out a mission,
do things he had no choice but to do,

245
00:20:05,234 --> 00:20:09,357
and take injuries he had to take,
would you blame him?

246
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:14,517
If it were for something that mattered,
of course not.

247
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:19,440
How you define "mattered" is hard to say.

248
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:23,520
I'm just worried about him.

249
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:27,060
As long as I'm at Haoyun, he'll be there.

250
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:31,080
As long as I'm in Teng City, he'll be on edge.

251
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:34,600
It's not that I don't trust him.
I just have to do something too.

252
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:37,120
I can't drag him down forever.

253
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:41,100
You're not dragging him down.

254
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:43,500
I watched both of you grow up.

255
00:20:43,500 --> 00:20:46,108
You both always think of each other.

256
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:51,000
Okay, enough of that.

257
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:53,740
Here. Have some soup. It's getting cold.

258
00:20:54,641 --> 00:20:57,600
I really didn't come here to play mediator.

259
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:00,260
Eat.

260
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:14,700
[Teng City Commercial Bank]
[The maturity proceeds of RMB 52,860]

261
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:20,320
What is it?

262
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:26,220
Someone sent me a gift.

263
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:31,635
Yi knows how things work.

264
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,981
<i>I was wrong before.</i>

265
00:21:48,981 --> 00:21:50,721
<i>You can move out if you want.</i>

266
00:21:50,721 --> 00:21:53,640
<i>I won't even stop you
if you choose to go back to Hai City.</i>

267
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:56,402
<i>But don't take risks.
I'm afraid I can't protect you.</i>

268
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:01,780
<i>You're not dragging him down.</i>

269
00:22:01,780 --> 00:22:04,770
<i>You both always think of each other.</i>

270
00:22:58,721 --> 00:23:00,400
Hello.

271
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:02,420
Hello. What can I help you with?

272
00:23:02,420 --> 00:23:03,820
I made an appointment by phone.

273
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:06,520
A policy of mine has matured.
I'd like to ask about it.

274
00:23:06,520 --> 00:23:08,700
Please show me your identification.

275
00:23:12,493 --> 00:23:14,100
Okay, I found it here.

276
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:17,340
You should receive a maturity payout
on August 19.

277
00:23:17,340 --> 00:23:19,661
The amount is 52,860 yuan.

278
00:23:19,661 --> 00:23:21,740
Can you look up the policyholder's details?

279
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:24,240
Sorry, ma'am.
We can't access policyholder details.

280
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:26,365
You'll need to ask the insurance company.

281
00:23:26,365 --> 00:23:28,279
Which insurance company?

282
00:23:28,279 --> 00:23:32,039
It says Peng City Huishou Insurance Company.

283
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:11,900
[Peng City to Teng City]

284
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:33,980
[Teng City Commercial Bank]
[The maturity proceeds of RMB 52,860]

285
00:25:11,660 --> 00:25:17,660
[Moments, Miao Jing]

286
00:25:46,140 --> 00:25:49,220
[Family, Miao, Keeping a record
makes the waiting feel less empty.]

287
00:25:49,220 --> 00:25:52,420
[You can request access below.
(Request Access)]

288
00:26:23,940 --> 00:26:26,740
What's wrong at the pool hall?
I'm on my way.

289
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:29,160
Can you see Miao Jing's social media feed?

290
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:39,780
Do you realize how insane it is
to call a newlywed man at two AM and ask

291
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:44,340
<i>if he can see the social feed
of a young, unmarried woman?</i>

292
00:26:44,340 --> 00:26:46,440
This is insane.

293
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:53,820
I know how to get you access.

294
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,580
What?

295
00:26:55,580 --> 00:26:59,729
Ask her yourself. Have her let you in.

296
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:04,661
Wish you a happy marriage. Go to sleep now.

297
00:27:04,661 --> 00:27:07,421
<i>You can't keep asking me every day.</i>

298
00:27:24,520 --> 00:27:27,700
[You can request access below.
(Request Access)]

299
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,179
Who is it?

300
00:28:19,361 --> 00:28:20,782
Yi.

301
00:28:24,207 --> 00:28:26,047
What are you doing here?

302
00:28:28,580 --> 00:28:30,901
I'm looking for Jing. Is she here with you?

303
00:28:30,901 --> 00:28:32,400
She's not here.

304
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:34,100
Let's talk outside.

305
00:28:36,620 --> 00:28:38,300
What were you thinking?

306
00:28:38,300 --> 00:28:40,640
Coming here to look for her?

307
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:43,306
Did Jing come back to Teng City?

308
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:47,424
What are you talking about?

309
00:28:47,424 --> 00:28:49,520
She's been in Teng City this whole time.

310
00:28:49,520 --> 00:28:51,360
Where else would she be?

311
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:53,245
Why are you looking for her again?

312
00:28:53,245 --> 00:28:56,940
Hasn't she been in Hai City?
We've been in touch all this time.

313
00:28:56,940 --> 00:29:00,820
If you can reach her, just call her directly.

314
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:02,402
Why come to me?

315
00:29:02,402 --> 00:29:05,600
I've called, but she won't pick up.

316
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:07,539
I...

317
00:29:07,539 --> 00:29:10,600
- I'm really worried about her.
- Worried about her?

318
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:14,620
Then why did you leave her with me?

319
00:29:19,681 --> 00:29:23,280
If you see Jing, send a message for me.

320
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:28,240
I came back this time
not to ask her for anything.

321
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:30,720
I came back just to see her.

322
00:29:32,860 --> 00:29:34,336
Yi.

323
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:43,280
You're still like brother and sister
to each other?

324
00:29:48,901 --> 00:29:50,390
What?

325
00:29:51,120 --> 00:29:55,838
When you left her behind,
did you never think about the fallout?

326
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:14,240
Yi, what brings you here?

327
00:30:15,140 --> 00:30:16,640
Help me get in touch.

328
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:20,167
Reach Fat Dragon and Ah Jiu for me.
What has Wei Ming Zhen been up to?

329
00:30:20,167 --> 00:30:21,300
Okay.

330
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:29,127
- Be on it!
- Be on it!

331
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:32,520
[Sunflower Kindergarten]
Left, right, left.

332
00:30:32,520 --> 00:30:34,481
Okay, let's go. Keep up.

333
00:30:34,481 --> 00:30:35,861
Keep up.

334
00:30:35,861 --> 00:30:37,520
- Keep up.
- Hold on.

335
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:40,080
Yes. Have him keep up.

336
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:42,359
Yang's mom is here.

337
00:30:46,564 --> 00:30:49,460
Yuan, Grandpa is here.

338
00:30:49,460 --> 00:30:51,520
- Cheng.
- Mom.

339
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:53,400
Grandma.

340
00:30:54,461 --> 00:30:55,760
Dad.

341
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:58,280
- Come here, come here.
- Yuan, over here.

342
00:30:59,141 --> 00:31:00,440
Over here.

343
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:01,780
Sis, look.

344
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:05,100
My teacher gave me this as a reward.
A red flower sticker.

345
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:06,560
You're amazing.

346
00:31:06,560 --> 00:31:08,560
Your teacher gave you a red flower?

347
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:10,000
- Yes.
- Let's go.

348
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:13,220
I'll take you out for a feast.
How does that sound?

349
00:31:13,861 --> 00:31:15,400
Let's go.

350
00:31:32,860 --> 00:31:35,880
[Teng City Commercial Bank]
[The maturity proceeds of RMB 52,860]

351
00:31:58,980 --> 00:32:04,500
[Jing, it's Mom. I'm back.
I've been missing you.]

352
00:32:58,620 --> 00:33:00,279
Thank you.

353
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:05,520
Don't feel pressured.

354
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:20,200
Monica backing off
isn't necessarily a bad thing.

355
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:25,560
She tried so hard to meddle before,
and now she's suddenly backing off.

356
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:28,520
Hai City must have found something else.

357
00:33:28,520 --> 00:33:30,941
We have a lead on the vacancy data.

358
00:33:30,941 --> 00:33:36,040
Haoyun's financial records show
a deeply buried funding gap.

359
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,780
That's right.

360
00:33:38,780 --> 00:33:40,580
Hongshen is pushing hard.

361
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:44,940
If Zhang Bin wants to cover the shortfall,
he'll have to make a move.

362
00:33:47,881 --> 00:33:49,141
- Zi Xin.
- Thank you, Yu.

363
00:33:49,141 --> 00:33:50,921
You get celebration candy too.

364
00:33:50,921 --> 00:33:52,381
Catch.

365
00:33:52,381 --> 00:33:53,600
- Here.
- Congratulations!

366
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:55,981
This is yours. Here is a pack for you.

367
00:33:55,981 --> 00:33:58,540
Jing, have some candy.

368
00:33:58,540 --> 00:34:00,181
Director Cen.

369
00:34:00,181 --> 00:34:01,540
You're getting married?

370
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:06,300
Who says a woman's good news
has to be marriage? I bought a house.

371
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:07,320
Congratulations.

372
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:09,380
Thank you.

373
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:13,720
Once we get back to Hai City,
I'll invite everyone to my place for hot pot.

374
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:15,421
- Great!
- It's a deal.

375
00:34:15,421 --> 00:34:20,280
That's our Yu!
When can I afford a place of my own?

376
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:22,460
Aren't you from Hai City?

377
00:34:22,460 --> 00:34:23,600
Yes.

378
00:34:23,600 --> 00:34:26,361
My parents wanted to transfer a house
under their name to me.

379
00:34:26,361 --> 00:34:29,564
But Cen, you know I don't want one.

380
00:34:29,564 --> 00:34:32,080
Otherwise, I'd have to obey them on everything.

381
00:34:32,080 --> 00:34:34,040
When to work, when to get married.

382
00:34:34,040 --> 00:34:36,821
If I did anything they didn't like, they'd say,

383
00:34:36,821 --> 00:34:40,300
"We gave you the house.
Why won't you listen to us?"

384
00:34:50,841 --> 00:34:54,240
The pieces we picked are pretty trendy.

385
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:56,861
Girls usually love them.

386
00:34:56,861 --> 00:34:59,619
- Could you try them on for me?
- Sure.

387
00:35:00,321 --> 00:35:02,780
This style is actually pretty trendy.

388
00:35:02,780 --> 00:35:05,600
Doesn't it dig into your hand?

389
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:08,780
It won't help to ask me.

390
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:12,420
Don't you know what styles your daughter likes?

391
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:15,901
Hi. I'd like to see this one.

392
00:35:15,901 --> 00:35:17,660
Take your time. Call me when you've picked one.

393
00:35:17,660 --> 00:35:18,480
Okay.

394
00:35:19,182 --> 00:35:22,589
- This one, right?
- Mom, I want this little bunny.

395
00:35:22,589 --> 00:35:26,660
You've got nerve, picking that.
Look at the price yourself.

396
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:28,400
You're not backing out, are you?

397
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:31,060
You promised me a piece of gold jewelry.

398
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:33,620
I want to pick one I actually like.

399
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:38,000
Fine. I must have owed you in a past life.

400
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:41,080
You are my daughter,
so I have to spoil you however much it takes.

401
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:44,080
- We'll take this one.
- Thank you, Mom.

402
00:35:52,720 --> 00:35:56,540
<i>She has slim wrists.
Bracelets look great on her.</i>

403
00:36:01,376 --> 00:36:03,600
<i>How about this one?</i>

404
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,640
<i>Hello?</i>

405
00:36:05,281 --> 00:36:07,741
<i>You rascal.</i>

406
00:36:07,741 --> 00:36:09,600
<i>- You rascal.
- Why don't you take another look?</i>

407
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:11,180
<i>See if anything else catches your eye.</i>

408
00:36:11,180 --> 00:36:12,640
<i>I'll wait at the intersection.</i>

409
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:15,620
<i>- How about this one?
- No, thank you.</i>

410
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:20,240
<i>- Sure.
- Let's try it on.</i>

411
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:23,000
<i>Jing.</i>

412
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:25,160
<i>I have to step out for something.</i>

413
00:36:25,160 --> 00:36:27,821
<i>Take the bus home later.</i>

414
00:36:27,821 --> 00:36:29,060
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

415
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,881
<i>- I'll come back in a couple of days.
- Okay.</i>

416
00:36:30,881 --> 00:36:32,700
<i>Be careful on your way home.</i>

417
00:36:33,361 --> 00:36:35,741
<i>Take a look and see
if there is anything you like.</i>

418
00:36:50,281 --> 00:36:53,520
If your budget is tight,
we also have some pendants.

419
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:55,961
Thread one on a cord,
and it looks about the same.

420
00:36:55,961 --> 00:36:59,590
It has to be a gold bracelet,
and it can't be too light.

421
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:01,881
I haven't seen my daughter in ages.

422
00:37:01,881 --> 00:37:03,143
Okay.

423
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:34,761
<i>The number you have dialed is powered off.</i>

424
00:37:34,761 --> 00:37:36,940
<i>Please try again later.</i>

425
00:38:37,560 --> 00:38:39,660
<i>Miao Jing, why are you still here?</i>

426
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:41,400
<i>Miss, I...</i>

427
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:43,020
<i>I filed a request with the school.</i>

428
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:45,160
<i>I applied for a winter break internship.</i>

429
00:38:45,160 --> 00:38:47,301
<i>What happened to you?</i>

430
00:38:47,301 --> 00:38:49,700
<i>Nothing. Just a bit of a cold.</i>

431
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:52,339
<i>Come on. Sit down. Sit.</i>

432
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:01,600
<i>You're burning up.
How can you do an internship?</i>

433
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:05,300
<i>Where's your family?
I'll call them to come pick you up.</i>

434
00:39:07,646 --> 00:39:10,020
<i>Wei Ming Zhen is your mother, right?</i>

435
00:39:10,020 --> 00:39:12,281
<i>Don't bother. You won't get through.</i>

436
00:39:12,281 --> 00:39:15,093
<i>How could I not get through?</i>

437
00:39:15,093 --> 00:39:17,369
<i>Did you have a fight with your family?</i>

438
00:39:17,369 --> 00:39:19,120
<i>Even so, they can't just leave you here.</i>

439
00:39:19,120 --> 00:39:21,680
<i>Hello? Who is this?</i>

440
00:39:21,680 --> 00:39:22,800
<i>Hello.</i>

441
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:26,120
<i>I'm an advisor
at Jiaohai University's business school.</i>

442
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:28,281
<i>- Are you Ms. Wei Ming Zhen?
- Wait, listen to me.</i>

443
00:39:28,281 --> 00:39:30,080
<i>If it isn't urgent, can you call back later?</i>

444
00:39:30,080 --> 00:39:32,020
<i>I'm busy right now.</i>

445
00:40:08,588 --> 00:40:09,841
Wait up.

446
00:40:09,841 --> 00:40:11,620
Hurry up.

447
00:40:16,020 --> 00:40:17,900
Are you okay?

448
00:40:19,261 --> 00:40:21,060
I only have two hours.

449
00:40:21,060 --> 00:40:23,160
Say what you need to say.

450
00:40:23,861 --> 00:40:26,068
Didn't you say two hours? Time's not up yet.

451
00:40:26,068 --> 00:40:28,251
Walk around with me first.

452
00:40:47,980 --> 00:40:53,540
I thought Teng City
would've changed a lot by now.

453
00:40:53,540 --> 00:40:56,560
I didn't expect these shops to still be here.

454
00:41:00,460 --> 00:41:06,346
That shop we just passed,
do you still remember it?

455
00:41:06,346 --> 00:41:11,261
In fifth grade, you got perfect scores on
both exams, so I took you there for a burger.

456
00:41:11,261 --> 00:41:13,272
Remember?

457
00:41:13,272 --> 00:41:14,520
Yeah.

458
00:41:14,520 --> 00:41:18,486
But you took a call and left
before you finished eating.

459
00:41:18,486 --> 00:41:21,040
I walked home by myself.

460
00:41:21,040 --> 00:41:22,720
And that wasn't the only time.

461
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:27,040
When you came back to see me in high school,
we met there too.

462
00:41:36,787 --> 00:41:40,186
If you have something to say, just say it.
Stop dancing around it.

463
00:41:44,660 --> 00:41:47,200
I just wanted to come back and see you.

464
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:49,756
And then?

465
00:41:50,441 --> 00:41:52,756
There has to be more to it than that.

466
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,900
It's true.

467
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:05,440
If you came back just to tell me this,

468
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:08,493
then you've said it, and we've met.

469
00:42:08,493 --> 00:42:10,685
You can go back now.

470
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:14,439
Where are you staying?
I'll have someone take you back.

471
00:42:15,261 --> 00:42:17,969
It's not yet two hours.

472
00:42:21,140 --> 00:42:23,240
Where are you going?

